---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';

const currentPath = Astro.url.pathname;
const lang = 'en';

const title = 'My Journey of Continuous Learning - Syaiful Anam';
const description = 'Follow my journey of continuous learning from designer to orchestrator, applying technology to create business impact.';
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} lang={lang}>
	<div class="container">
		<Header currentPath={currentPath} lang={lang} />

		<main class="main-content">
			<div class="journey-content">
				<h1>My Journey of Continuous Learning</h1>

				<p class="intro">
					Technology has been my constant companion throughout my career. Each phase has taught me valuable lessons
					that I carry forward, building upon previous experiences to create meaningful impact.
				</p>

				<div class="timeline">
					<div class="timeline-item">
						<div class="timeline-marker">1</div>
						<div class="timeline-content">
							<h2>The Designer (CorelDRAW)</h2>
							<div class="timeline-period">2015 - 2017</div>
							<p>
								My journey began with visual design. I learned the principles of composition, color theory,
								and user experience through creating graphics and marketing materials. This foundation taught me
								the importance of aesthetics and how design choices impact user perception.
							</p>
							<ul class="learnings">
								<li>Visual composition and design principles</li>
								<li>Understanding user experience</li>
								<li>Client communication and requirement gathering</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="timeline-item">
						<div class="timeline-marker">2</div>
						<div class="timeline-content">
							<h2>The Implementer (WordPress)</h2>
							<div class="timeline-period">2017 - 2019</div>
							<p>
								Transitioning from static designs to dynamic websites, I embraced WordPress and PHP development.
								This phase taught me how websites function under the hood, the importance of database design,
								and how to create custom solutions that meet specific business needs.
							</p>
							<ul class="learnings">
								<li>Web development fundamentals (HTML, CSS, JavaScript)</li>
								<li>PHP and WordPress custom development</li>
								<li>Database design and management</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="timeline-item">
						<div class="timeline-marker">3</div>
						<div class="timeline-content">
							<h2>The Architect (Laravel)</h2>
							<div class="timeline-period">2019 - 2022</div>
							<p>
								As projects grew in complexity, I moved to Laravel and embraced modern PHP practices.
								This period shaped my understanding of software architecture, clean code principles,
								and how to build scalable applications that can grow with business needs.
							</p>
							<ul class="learnings">
								<li>Modern PHP frameworks and OOP principles</li>
								<li>RESTful API design and development</li>
								<li>System architecture and scalability</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="timeline-item">
						<div class="timeline-marker">4</div>
						<div class="timeline-content">
							<h2>The Orchestrator (AI & Next.js)</h2>
							<div class="timeline-period">2022 - Present</div>
							<p>
								Currently, I'm exploring how AI can enhance the development lifecycle. Working with Next.js,
								modern JavaScript frameworks, and AI tools has opened up new possibilities for creating
								intelligent, efficient, and user-centric solutions.
							</p>
							<ul class="learnings">
								<li>AI-driven development and automation</li>
								<li>Modern JavaScript ecosystems (Next.js, React)</li>
								<li>DevOps and cloud deployment strategies</li>
							</ul>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="conclusion">
					<h2>The Journey Continues</h2>
					<p>
						Each phase builds upon the last, creating a unique perspective that combines design thinking,
						technical expertise, and business acumen. I'm constantly learning and adapting, ready for the
						next chapter in this ever-evolving technology landscape.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer lang={lang} />
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>
	.main-content {
		min-height: calc(100vh - 200px);
	}

	.journey-content {
		padding: var(--spacing-xl) 0;
	}

	.intro {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
		margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
		text-align: center;
		max-width: 600px;
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
	}

	.timeline {
		position: relative;
		margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
	}

	.timeline::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		top: 0;
		bottom: 0;
		width: 2px;
		background-color: var(--color-border);
	}

	.timeline-item {
		position: relative;
		padding-left: var(--spacing-xl);
		margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xl);
	}

	.timeline-marker {
		position: absolute;
		left: -15px;
		top: 0;
		width: 32px;
		height: 32px;
		background-color: var(--color-accent);
		color: white;
		border-radius: 50%;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		font-weight: 600;
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		border: 3px solid var(--color-background);
		z-index: 1;
	}

	.timeline-content {
		background-color: var(--color-surface);
		border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
		border-radius: 12px;
		padding: var(--spacing-lg);
		transition: all 0.3s ease;
	}

	.timeline-content:hover {
		transform: translateX(4px);
		border-color: var(--color-accent);
	}

	.timeline-content h2 {
		margin-top: 0;
		margin-bottom: var(--spacing-xs);
		color: var(--color-text);
	}

	.timeline-period {
		color: var(--color-accent);
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		font-weight: 600;
		margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
	}

	.timeline-content p {
		margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
	}

	.learnings {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.learnings li {
		padding: var(--spacing-xs) 0;
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
		position: relative;
		padding-left: var(--spacing-md);
	}

	.learnings li::before {
		content: 'â†’';
		position: absolute;
		left: 0;
		color: var(--color-accent);
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.conclusion {
		background-color: var(--color-surface);
		border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
		border-radius: 12px;
		padding: var(--spacing-xl);
		text-align: center;
		margin-top: var(--spacing-xl);
	}

	.conclusion h2 {
		margin-top: 0;
		margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
		color: var(--color-text);
	}

	.conclusion p {
		font-size: 1.125rem;
		color: var(--color-text-secondary);
		margin-bottom: 0;
	}

	/* Responsive design */
	@media (max-width: 768px) {
		.journey-content {
			padding: var(--spacing-lg) 0;
		}

		.timeline::before {
			left: var(--spacing-sm);
		}

		.timeline-item {
			padding-left: var(--spacing-2xl);
		}

		.timeline-marker {
			left: calc(var(--spacing-sm) - 15px);
		}

		.timeline-content {
			padding: var(--spacing-md);
		}

		.timeline-content:hover {
			transform: none;
		}
	}
</style>